OL,3,CWater firm to use AI to stop toxic
OL,4,Cpellets spilling into sea
OL,6,FSouthern Water says it is going to use
OL,7,FArtificial Intelligence to detect
OL,8,Ftoxic plastic pellets in its
OL,9,Fwastewater, to stop them spilling into
OL,10,Fthe sea.
OL,12,FIt follows an incident in October last
OL,13,Fyear when millions of bio-beads, used
OL,14,Fin the treatment of wastewater,
OL,15,Fspilled from a Southern Water plant in
OL,16,FEastbourne, threatening an
OL,17,Fenvironmental disaster.
