OL,3,CWater firm to use AI to stop toxic
OL,4,Cpellets spilling into sea
OL,6,FSouthern Water have been cleaning up
OL,7,Fthe beach at Camber, East Sussex, on
OL,8,FFriday (6 February) and says it is
OL,9,Fcommitted to cleaning up the beaches
OL,10,Ffor the next three years.
OL,12,FTeams have been sifting and removing,
OL,13,Fbio-beads, microplastics, and other
OL,14,Fpollution like fishing nets from the
OL,15,Fsand.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
