OL,4,Cpellets spilling into sea
OL,6,FThey have collected almost two tonnes
OL,7,Fout of waste in total, just under half
OL,8,Fthe amount of bio-beads which were
OL,9,Freleased. They aim to make the beach
OL,10,Fcleaner than it was before this
OL,11,Fenvironmental disaster.
OL,13,FAnne-Marie McDonald, Southern Water
OL,14,Fsaid: "We're fully committed to
OL,15,Fpreventing any more spill of bio-beads
OL,16,Fby using all of the latest innovative
OL,17,Ftechnology and engineering solutions.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
