OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F411A1770476501
OL,3,CWater firm to use AI to stop toxic
OL,4,Cpellets spilling into sea
OL,6,F"So we've got cameras now downstairs
OL,7,Fin Eastbourne, which is fully
OL,8,Funderground, it's the size of the Amex
OL,9,Fstadium, 14 metres underground.
OL,11,F"We've got cameras trained to see if
OL,12,Fthe beads are moving around.
OL,14,F"The bit that we're innovating on now
OL,15,Fis using AI and machine learning
OL,16,Ftechnology to proactively identify any
OL,17,Fabnormality that will enable the team
OL,18,Fto automatically switch off the
OL,19,Fprocess unit without even having to go
OL,20,Fdownstairs."
