OL,3,CWater firm to use AI to stop toxic
OL,4,Cpellets spilling into sea
OL,6,FA firm based in Medway, Kent,
OL,7,Fdeveloped the kit in just two months,
OL,8,Fin direct response to bio-bead crisis.
OL,10,FIt uses GPS technology to track which
OL,11,Fareas have been covered, and will be
OL,12,Fkey to Southern Water's pledge to keep
OL,13,Fcleaning the spill until 2029.
OL,15,FSouthern Water uses bio-beads at five
OL,16,Fout of their 367 treatment works, they
OL,17,Finclude Eastbourne, Peacehaven,
OL,18,FBeckley near Rye, Broomfield Bank near
OL,19,FDover and on the Isle of Wight.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
