OL,4,Cpellets spilling into sea
OL,6,FDespite the company spending millions
OL,7,Fon the clear-up, it says it would cost
OL,8,Fmuch more to convert the ageing
OL,9,Fwastewater facilities where bio-beads
OL,10,Fare used.
OL,12,FThe MP for Hastings and Rye, Helena
OL,13,FDollimore has little sympathy for that
OL,14,Fargument, she is part of the calls for
OL,15,Ftheir to be a legal ban on the use of
OL,16,Fbio-beads
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
