OL,6,FThat would require a law change
OL,7,Fthrough parliament and she is actively
OL,8,Ftrying to gain enough signatures on a
OL,9,Fpetition so the issue can receive a
OL,10,FGovernment response.
OL,12,FSouthern Water, however, says it would
OL,13,Fnot be logistically or economically
OL,14,Ffeasible to change the methods at
OL,15,Ftheir plants where bio-beads are used.
OL,17,FSouthern Water could still face
OL,18,Fconsequences for the environmental
OL,19,Fmess it has created, as an Environment
OL,20,FAgency investigation ongoing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
