OL,4,Cpellets spilling into sea
OL,6,FAn Environment Agency spokesman said:
OL,7,F"We acknowledge that Southern Water
OL,8,Fadmitted responsibility for the
OL,9,Fpollution incident at Camber Sands in
OL,10,FNovember.
OL,12,F"This is an active investigation, and
OL,13,Fwe will not hesitate to take robust
OL,14,Fenforcement action where appropriate.
OL,16,F"We continue to work closely with
OL,17,FRother District Council and other
OL,18,Fagencies following the incident. The
OL,19,Fcouncil remains the lead authority for
OL,20,Fthe clean-up, and we remain ready to
OL,21,Fhelp should they need it.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
